headline: KeyBanc bumps Eaton stock to 'overweight' on growth in electrification, aerospace
summary: Investing.com -- KeyBanc Capital Markets upgraded Eaton (NYSE:ETN) Corp to “Overweight” with a $340 price target on company’s strong growth prospects in electrification and aerospace sector offsetting concerns over data center capital spending.
